# The “Proof Pack” (What to screenshot for portfolio / interview)

Take screenshots of:

1. Policy assignment at **Management Group scope**
2. A denied deployment error (missing tag / wrong region)
3. Private DNS resolution output (private IP)
4. Firewall log entry showing Dev VM traffic
5. Log Analytics workspace showing collected logs
6. Defender for Cloud secure score (optional)

This becomes your evidence.

