# Simple Pass/Fail Checklist (Dev)

You can literally tick these:

* [ ] Tags required policy blocks untagged resource
* [ ] Allowed locations blocks non-Canada region
* [ ] Public IP creation blocked or audited
* [ ] Storage/Key Vault public access blocked or audited
* [ ] Dev VM outbound traffic goes through firewall (logs prove)
* [ ] Storage/Key Vault accessible privately via private endpoint
* [ ] DNS resolves to private IP
* [ ] Logs from Dev resources appear in central Log Analytics

